				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1. Teleport there \"goto -124.84, 3.94, 95.70\"\r\nor\r\n1. Saved bookmark is \"Kidnappers Cave\".\r\n2. Run into the nearby cave.\r\n3. Be spotted by the either the Smugglers or Attackers."
